<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>TrmWordDict — 컴포넌트 구조</title>
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #0f172a; color: #e2e8f0; padding: 32px; }
  h1 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #f8fafc; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .subtitle { font-size: 13px; color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 32px; }

  .tree { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
  .node { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0; }
  .children { margin-left: 24px; border-left: 1px dashed #334155; }
  .connector {
    width: 24px; min-width: 24px; height: 32px;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed #334155;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .box {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    padding: 5px 12px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500;
    margin: 3px 0; white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .box .path { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 400; opacity: 0.6; margin-left: 4px; }
  .box .badge {
    font-size: 10px; padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 3px;
    font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .entry    { background: #1e3a5f; border: 1px solid #2563eb; color: #93c5fd; }
  .entry .badge { background: #2563eb; color: #fff; }
  .provider { background: #1a2e1a; border: 1px solid #16a34a; color: #86efac; }
  .provider .badge { background: #16a34a; color: #fff; }
  .router   { background: #2d1f3d; border: 1px solid #7c3aed; color: #c4b5fd; }
  .router .badge { background: #7c3aed; color: #fff; }
  .layout   { background: #1e2d3d; border: 1px solid #0284c7; color: #7dd3fc; }
  .layout .badge { background: #0284c7; color: #fff; }
  .guard    { background: #3d2b1a; border: 1px solid #d97706; color: #fcd34d; }
  .guard .badge { background: #d97706; color: #fff; }
  .page     { background: #1e1b2e; border: 1px solid #6d28d9; color: #ddd6fe; }
  .page .badge { background: #6d28d9; color: #fff; }
  .shared   { background: #1f2937; border: 1px solid #374151; color: #9ca3af; }
  .shared .badge { background: #374151; color: #d1d5db; }
  .store    { background: #2d1f1f; border: 1px solid #dc2626; color: #fca5a5; }
  .store .badge { background: #dc2626; color: #fff; }
  .external { background: #1a1a2e; border: 1px solid #4f46e5; color: #a5b4fc; font-style: italic; }

  .route-label {
    font-size: 11px; color: #475569; margin: 2px 0 2px 24px;
    padding-left: 12px; border-left: 1px dashed #1e3a5f;
  }

  .cols { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 48px; align-items: start; }
  h2 { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #94a3b8; margin-bottom: 14px;
       text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
  .section { margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .note { font-size: 11px; color: #475569; margin-top: 4px; margin-left: 12px; font-style: italic; }

  .legend {
    display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; margin-top: 40px;
    padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #1e293b;
  }
  .legend-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: 12px; color: #64748b; }
  .legend-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 2px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>TrmWordDict — 컴포넌트 구조</h1>
<p class="subtitle">React 18 + Vite 5 + shadcn/ui &nbsp;|&nbsp; 2026-05-18</p>

<div class="cols">

<!-- LEFT: 진입점 ~ 라우터 -->
<div>
  <h2>진입점 &amp; 라우터 트리</h2>

  <div class="tree">
    <div class="box entry">
      <span class="badge">Entry</span>
      main.jsx
      <span class="path">src/main.jsx</span>
    </div>
    <div class="children">

      <div class="node"><div class="connector"></div>
        <div>
          <div class="box provider">
            <span class="badge">Provider</span>
            &lt;Providers /&gt;
            <span class="path">src/app/providers.jsx</span>
          </div>
          <div class="children">

            <div class="node"><div class="connector"></div>
              <div class="box external">&lt;QueryClientProvider&gt; — TanStack Query v5</div>
            </div>

            <div class="node"><div class="connector"></div>
              <div>
                <div class="box router">
                  <span class="badge">Router</span>
                  &lt;RouterProvider&gt; createBrowserRouter
                  <span class="path">src/app/router.jsx</span>
                </div>
                <div class="children">

                  <!-- BlankLayout -->
                  <div class="node"><div class="connector"></div>
                    <div>
                      <div class="box layout">
                        <span class="badge">Layout</span>
                        &lt;BlankLayout /&gt;
                        <span class="path">src/layouts/BlankLayout.jsx</span>
                      </div>
                      <div class="route-label">path: /login</div>
                      <div class="children">
                        <div class="node"><div class="connector"></div>
                          <div class="box page">
                            <span class="badge">Page</span>
                            &lt;LoginPage /&gt;
                            <span class="path">src/features/auth/LoginPage.jsx</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <!-- ProtectedRoute -->
                  <div class="node"><div class="connector"></div>
                    <div>
                      <div class="box guard">
                        <span class="badge">Guard</span>
                        &lt;ProtectedRoute /&gt;
                        <span class="path">src/router/ProtectedRoute.jsx</span>
                      </div>
                      <div class="children">
                        <div class="node"><div class="connector"></div>
                          <div>
                            <div class="box layout">
                              <span class="badge">Layout</span>
                              &lt;MainLayout /&gt;
                              <span class="path">src/layouts/MainLayout.jsx</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="children">

                              <!-- HomePage -->
                              <div class="node"><div class="connector"></div>
                                <div>
                                  <div class="box page"><span class="badge">Page</span>&lt;HomePage /&gt;<span class="path">src/features/home/HomePage.jsx</span></div>
                                  <div class="route-label">path: /home</div>
                                </div>
                              </div>

                              <!-- UploadPage -->
                              <div class="node"><div class="connector"></div>
                                <div>
                                  <div class="box page"><span class="badge">Page</span>&lt;UploadPage /&gt;<span class="path">src/features/import/UploadPage.jsx</span></div>
                                  <div class="route-label">path: /import</div>
                                  <div class="children">
                                    <div class="node"><div class="connector"></div>
                                      <div class="box shared"><span class="badge">UI</span>&lt;FileUpload /&gt;</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="node"><div class="connector"></div>
                                      <div class="box shared"><span class="badge">UI</span>&lt;Button /&gt; (shadcn)</div>
                                    </div>
                                  </div>
                                </div>
                              </div>

                              <!-- DetailPage -->
                              <div class="node"><div class="connector"></div>
                                <div>
                                  <div class="box page"><span class="badge">Page</span>&lt;DetailPage /&gt;<span class="path">src/features/import/DetailPage.jsx</span></div>
                                  <div class="route-label">path: /import/:historyId</div>
                                  <div class="children">
                                    <div class="node"><div class="connector"></div>
                                      <div class="box shared"><span class="badge">UI</span>&lt;DataGrid /&gt; (오류 목록, polling)</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="node"><div class="connector"></div>
                                      <div class="box shared"><span class="badge">UI</span>&lt;DetailPanel /&gt;</div>
                                    </div>
                                  </div>
                                </div>
                              </div>

                              <!-- DomainListPage -->
                              <div class="node"><div class="connector"></div>
                                <div>
                                  <div class="box page"><span class="badge">Page</span>&lt;DomainListPage /&gt;<span class="path">src/features/domain/DomainListPage.jsx</span></div>
                                  <div class="route-label">path: /domain</div>
                                  <div class="children">
                                    <div class="node"><div class="connector"></div>
                                      <div class="box shared"><span class="badge">UI</span>&lt;SearchForm /&gt;</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="node"><div class="connector"></div>
                                      <div class="box shared"><span class="badge">UI</span>&lt;DataGrid /&gt; (도메인 목록)</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="node"><div class="connector"></div>
                                      <div>
                                        <div class="box shared"><span class="badge">UI</span>&lt;DetailPanel /&gt; (우측 패널)</div>
                                        <div class="children">
                                          <div class="node"><div class="connector"></div>
                                            <div class="box shared"><span class="badge">UI</span>&lt;EditDrawer /&gt; (Sheet 기반)</div>
                                          </div>
                                        </div>
                                      </div>
                                    </div>
                                  </div>
                                </div>
                              </div>

                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div><!-- /ProtectedRoute -->

                </div>
              </div>
            </div><!-- /RouterProvider -->

            <div class="node"><div class="connector"></div>
              <div class="box external">&lt;Toaster /&gt; — sonner</div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div><!-- /Providers -->

    </div>
  </div><!-- /tree -->

  <div style="margin-top: 20px; padding: 12px 14px; border: 1px dashed #334155; border-radius: 6px;">
    <div class="box entry" style="opacity:0.55; border-style:dashed; font-size:12px;">
      <span class="badge">Entry</span>
      App.jsx (미사용)
      <span class="path">src/App.jsx</span>
    </div>
    <p class="note">main.jsx가 Providers를 직접 렌더링하므로 App.jsx는 실행되지 않음.<br>
    내부의 AppRouter(BrowserRouter)는 중복 라우터 — 삭제 가능.</p>
  </div>

</div>

<!-- RIGHT: 공유 컴포넌트 & 상태 -->
<div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>공유 컴포넌트</h2>

    <div class="box shared" style="margin-bottom:4px;">
      <span class="badge">UI</span>DataGrid
      <span class="path">src/shared/components/DataGrid/DataGrid.jsx</span>
    </div>
    <p class="note">shadcn Table 래퍼. columns + data props.</p>

    <div class="box shared" style="margin: 8px 0 4px;">
      <span class="badge">UI</span>SearchForm
      <span class="path">src/shared/components/SearchForm/SearchForm.jsx</span>
    </div>
    <p class="note">Input(shadcn) + Button(shadcn). onSearch 콜백.</p>

    <div class="box shared" style="margin: 8px 0 4px;">
      <span class="badge">UI</span>FileUpload
      <span class="path">src/shared/components/FileUpload/FileUpload.jsx</span>
    </div>
    <p class="note">드래그앤드롭 + 파일 선택. accept / onFileSelect props.</p>

    <div class="box shared" style="margin: 8px 0 4px;">
      <span class="badge">UI</span>DetailPanel
      <span class="path">src/shared/components/DetailPanel/DetailPanel.jsx</span>
    </div>
    <p class="note">우측 고정 패널. 선택 행의 상세 데이터 표시.</p>

    <div class="box shared" style="margin: 8px 0 4px;">
      <span class="badge">UI</span>EditDrawer
      <span class="path">src/shared/components/EditDrawer/EditDrawer.jsx</span>
    </div>
    <p class="note">Sheet(shadcn) 기반 우측 슬라이드 서랍.<br>SheetHeader + SheetBody + SheetFooter 구조.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>shadcn/ui 프리미티브</h2>
    <div class="box external" style="margin-bottom:4px;">Button — Radix Slot + cva (variant / size)</div>
    <div class="box external" style="margin-bottom:4px;">Input — border-input CSS variable</div>
    <div class="box external" style="margin-bottom:4px;">Table / TableHeader / TableRow / TableCell …</div>
    <div class="box external" style="margin-bottom:4px;">Sheet — Radix Dialog + cva (side: right / left / top / bottom)</div>
    <p class="note">src/shared/components/ui/ 위치. shadcn CLI 복사 방식 (npm 패키지 아님).</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>전역 상태 (Zustand)</h2>
    <div class="box store">
      <span class="badge">Store</span>useAuthStore
      <span class="path">src/store/authStore.js</span>
    </div>
    <p class="note">isAuthenticated · user · token<br>
    ProtectedRoute → 인증 확인<br>
    LoginPage → login() 호출<br>
    MainLayout → logout() 호출</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>서버 상태 (TanStack Query)</h2>
    <div class="box external" style="margin-bottom:4px;">useDomainList — GET /api/v1/domain</div>
    <div class="box external" style="margin-bottom:4px;">useImportJobDetail — GET /api/v1/import/:id (polling)</div>
    <div class="box external" style="margin-bottom:4px;">useUploadMutation — POST /api/v1/import</div>
    <p class="note">src/features/{module}/hooks/ 또는 api/ 위치.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>데이터 흐름</h2>
    <div style="font-size:12px; color:#64748b; line-height:2;">
      <p>① <span style="color:#7dd3fc">main.jsx</span> → Providers 마운트 (QueryClient + Router + Toaster)</p>
      <p>② <span style="color:#fcd34d">ProtectedRoute</span> → useAuthStore 확인 → 미인증 시 /login 리다이렉트</p>
      <p>③ <span style="color:#7dd3fc">MainLayout</span> → 사이드바 Nav + Outlet으로 페이지 교체</p>
      <p>④ Page → <span style="color:#a5b4fc">TanStack Query hooks</span>로 API 호출 → DataGrid · DetailPanel에 props 전달</p>
      <p>⑤ 수정 요청 → <span style="color:#9ca3af">EditDrawer</span>(Sheet) 폼 → useMutation → invalidateQueries</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
</div><!-- /cols -->

<div class="legend">
  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:#2563eb;"></div>진입점</div>
  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:#16a34a;"></div>Provider</div>
  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:#7c3aed;"></div>Router</div>
  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:#0284c7;"></div>Layout</div>
  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:#d97706;"></div>Guard (인증)</div>
  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:#6d28d9;"></div>Page</div>
  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:#374151;"></div>공유 컴포넌트</div>
  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:#dc2626;"></div>Store (Zustand)</div>
  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:#4f46e5;"></div>외부 라이브러리</div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
